snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Chaos Gate - Daemonhunters - Duty Eternal | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy now: https://www.chaosgate.com/dlc/duty-eternal

Experience thrilling new missions, powerful additional classes, and all-new ways to decimate the forces of Nurgle in the first major DLC for the critically-acclaimed tactical turn-based RPG.

Out now!

Find out more at www.chaosgate.com/dutyeternal
